The purpose of this app is for a user to be able to provide code and get an AI explanation in plain English that is understandable to a lay person. It should have the following features:
- User can paste blocks of code OR upload code files 
- App detects code language
- User submits code and:
    - App gives a line-by-line breakdown of what each line of code is doing 
    - App gives a summary of how the full block of code/code file
    - App also gives some additional links for 'further reading' for the user
